            ("场景 B：分桶抗热 Key", "### 问题\n```\n热门商品（如 iPhone 15）—— 所有请求打同一个 Redis key\nRedis 单线程 → 热点 key 成为瓶颈\n```\n\n### 分桶方案\n```java\n// 库存 10000 → 分成 10 个桶，每桶 1000\npublic class BucketStockService {\n    private final int BUCKET_COUNT = 10;\n    \n    public boolean deduct(Long userId, String productId, int amount) {\n        // 1. 随机选择一个桶尝试\n        int bucketId = ThreadLocalRandom.current().nextInt(BUCKET_COUNT);\n        String bucketKey = \"stock:\" + productId + \":bucket:\" + bucketId;\n        \n        Long remain = redisTemplate.opsForValue().decrement(bucketKey, amount);\n        \n        if (remain >= 0) return true;  // 扣减成功\n        \n        // 2. 当前桶不够，尝试其他桶\n        redisTemplate.opsForValue().increment(bucketKey, amount);  // 回补\n        \n        for (int i = 0; i < BUCKET_COUNT; i++) {\n            String otherBucket = \"stock:\" + productId + \":bucket:\" + i;\n            remain = redisTemplate.opsForValue().decrement(otherBucket, amount);\n            if (remain >= 0) return true;\n            redisTemplate.opsForValue().increment(otherBucket, amount);\n        }\n        \n        return false;  // 所有桶都不够\n    }\n}\n```"),
