            ("场景 A：ConcurrentHashMap 实现缓存（简化版）", "```java\npublic class SimpleCache<K, V> {\n    private final Map<K, V> cache = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();\n    private final Map<K, Long> expireAt = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();\n    private final int maxSize;\n    \n    public SimpleCache(int maxSize) {\n        this.maxSize = maxSize;\n    }\n    \n    public V get(K key) {\n        Long exp = expireAt.get(key);\n        if (exp != null && exp < System.currentTimeMillis()) {\n            remove(key);  // 懒清理\n            return null;\n        }\n        return cache.get(key);\n    }\n    \n    public void put(K key, V value, long ttlSeconds) {\n        if (cache.size() >= maxSize) {\n            // 简化版淘汰：随机删除一个（生产用 LRU）\n            K randomKey = cache.keySet().iterator().next();\n            remove(randomKey);\n        }\n        cache.put(key, value);\n        expireAt.put(key, System.currentTimeMillis() + ttlSeconds * 1000);\n    }\n    \n    private void remove(K key) {\n        cache.remove(key);\n        expireAt.remove(key);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**问题**：淘汰策略太简单，没有 LRU/LFU。实际生产用 Guava Cache 或 Caffeine。"),
            ("场景 B：LRU 淘汰算法实现", "```java\n// 线程安全的 LRU 缓存（用 ReadWriteLock）\npublic class LruCache<K, V> {\n    private final int maxSize;\n    private final Map<K, Node<K, V>> map;\n    private final Node<K, V> head, tail;  // 双向链表\n    private final ReadWriteLock lock = new ReentrantReadWriteLock();\n    \n    // 访问时移到队尾（最久未使用在队头）\n    public V get(K key) {\n        lock.readLock().lock();\n        try {\n            Node<K, V> node = map.get(key);\n            if (node != null) {\n                moveToTail(node);  // 移到队尾（最近使用）\n                return node.value;\n            }\n            return null;\n        } finally {\n            lock.readLock().unlock();\n        }\n    }\n    \n    // 插入时检查容量，超过则删除队头\n    public void put(K key, V value) {\n        lock.writeLock().lock();\n        try {\n            Node<K, V> node = map.get(key);\n            if (node != null) {\n                node.value = value;\n                moveToTail(node);\n            } else {\n                node = new Node<>(key, value);\n                map.put(key, node);\n                addToTail(node);\n                \n                if (map.size() > maxSize) {\n                    Node<K, V> removed = removeHead();  // 淘汰最久未使用\n                    map.remove(removed.key);\n                }\n            }\n        } finally {\n            lock.writeLock().unlock();\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Caffeine 方案**：用 `ConcurrentHashMap` + W-TinyLFU 算法，无锁读，性能碾压上面的方案。面试直接说「生产用 Caffeine」。"),
